# Cloudflare credentials for the WE-site deploy (#1137). Copy to `.cloudflare.env` (gitignored) and fill in.
# Claude sources this per wrangler command so the token never enters the chat or shell history.
#
# Scoped API token — create at Cloudflare → My Profile → API Tokens → Create Token → Custom.
# Permissions needed for Claude to manage the whole Cloudflare side (see the deploy runbook):
#   - Account · Cloudflare Pages · Edit      (deploy + secrets + attach custom domain to the Pages project)
#   - Zone · DNS · Edit                       (create/manage DNS records once the domain is a CF zone)
#   - Zone · Zone · Read                      (read zone status; required to attach the custom domain)
#   - Account · Zone · Edit  (OPTIONAL)        (only if you want Claude to CREATE the zone via API rather
#                                               than clicking "Add a site" in the dashboard yourself)
# Set a short expiry and revoke it when the deploy work is done.
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
